{
  "stem": "13693.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The first-- the first encounter with what I have was-- is in here, is they told me to take the-- to take the-- the horses back.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was [NON-ENGLISH], this means I got the food, and they brought in the-- brought in the-- the supplies.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had to bring back-- back-- the-- the horses and the wagons back to the people what we took-- what we made the requisition.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Second requisition.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't pay for it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Peasant, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I brought in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We come into the country-- on the beginning of the village and suddenly [CRASHING SOUNDS] from there-- from a bullet.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I jumped off from there-- from the wagons, and we go back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we start to run back on-- on foot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, next day the German came in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Goes-- go through our-- to our area.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The captain made an ambush.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He killed-- killed one German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And since that times, this was our area.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And gradually it was starting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We have to develop-- what I heard yesterday-- we developed this psychology of war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had-- we had psychology of respect for human dignity.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The-- the Goyem have a respect for-- for power.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this is Nietzsche.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Nietzsche in here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "War is the ultimate achievement of improvement of human life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so the thing is gradually you have the transformation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Next, a few days later, they send us to cut-- cut the electrical poles.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And a few days later, finally on the six- six weeks, eight weeks you are already graduating to put some mines.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And now we can tell a few stories in order to bring it in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] is this is a hamlet or a village what was on the-- on our road.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
